Bsed is a simple binary stream editor that can do substitutions on binary
files.  See "toolman bsed" for details.

Bsed is now available in World-Wide Exptools, with a home page of
    http://www.bell-labs.com/wwexptools/bsed/

If you have any questions or suggestions, contact the author
Dave Dykstra <dwd@bell-labs.com>.
